race.description: City Motors Group Midway Maiden Plate
race.comment: Going with the race experience of the speedy KISSAVOS (3) who produced a career-best performance last start at Wyong, beaten by the barest margin over today's trip after a desperate battle in the straight. Beautifully drawn and looks a great chance to go one better. MRS FLANDERS (11) is an Anders filly on debut for local trainer Kerry Parker. Recently switched to his stable from Waterhouse/Bott and won a trial on her home track. One to keep in mind. CENTURY SONG (1) is back from a six-month spell. Raced just once last prep and was disappointing as firm favourite. Won a recent trial so might be able to put the record straight. CAPTIVATING TYCOON (2) has shown good signs at the trials this time in work and profiles nicely for the Freedman yard.
